s/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  返去讀小學啦，幼稚到。。。想食蛋糕咪一齊去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係咁 重點係無買唔緊要 做咩要講大話先？</blockquote><br />\n試下諗下佢經濟 工作時間 社交圈子最近有冇問題？<br />\n好多時大話背後有好多對方諗過度過先講<br />\n當然 可能係懶 唔撚記得左都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係根本好小事 反而留意下佢最近有冇唔妥 有冇咩地方雙方缺乏溝通仲好"},{"pid":"169c3e6df16466b6aa53ac1dd09a6b1b57f779c0","tid":396842,"uid":26592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:06:45.000Z","msg":"小事就算啦<br />\n大事就了解完件事 同佢傾傾<br />\n佢唔肯傾既你講下你既懷疑（當然要基於一d根據）<br />\n雖然係誤會既話會傷感情 不過好過日後先爆"},{"pid":"836b6c83615208cbf8889f2987b552251a74e4d4","tid":396842,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:35:34.000Z","msg":"或者咁講 可能你會話 好少事姐 小學雞<br />\n但我份人係會嬲 但好過我發現你講大話嬲我<br />\n<br />\n同埋 其實可以反映到處事手法<br />\n可能下次會話 我唔話比你聽約左某個人 都係唔想你唔開心姐<br />\n我唔想比你睇對話 係唔想你唔開心姐<br />\n我刪對話 廢事你唔開心姐<br />\n<br />\n雖然上面個例子係我身上發生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我寧願你誠實啲講 都好過比我知你講大話<br />\n<br />\n大話就係大話 邊有分善唔善意"},{"pid":"f212325b369db5ff14cba3ebe6a361eec598b797","tid":396842,"uid":68864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"善乜撚意<br />\n佢為咗掩飾自己冇心準時買咋，想自己唔畀人嬲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係想樓主冇咁唔開心咩<br />\n殊不知樓主都唔會嬲咁小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你要講大話先嬲咋"},{"pid":"ab98cb1fa6dc652948e4bfd2142662d249152778","tid":396842,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>善乜撚意<br />\n佢為咗掩飾自己冇心準時買咋，想自己唔畀人嬲咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係想樓主冇咁唔開心咩<br />\n殊不知樓主都唔會嬲咁小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你要講大話先嬲咋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f949188d2d6e20ee31f75cb57b145306933149d","tid":396842,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:04:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c14a104e784d6fe08cb4bf5cf9317b86ae962d1","tid":396842,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁少事都呃你 即係呃你已經係家常便飯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能啦"}]}